## 10. Observability

<!-- Required: every new code path either emits telemetry or has a justification why not. -->

| Concern | Plan |
|---|---|
| Langfuse spans | Span name(s) emitted, attributes captured (PII-safe), where in the code |
| Metrics | Counters / histograms added (latency, error count, business KPI) |
| Logs | New structured log fields. NO PII. NO secrets. |
| Alerts | New alert rules (Sentry / Grafana). Threshold + ownership. |
| Dashboards | Existing dashboards updated, new dashboards added |
| Trace context | sessionId / userId / requestId propagation through new modules |

If this change introduces an LLM call: spans MUST tag `model`, `input_token_count`, `output_token_count`, `cost_usd_estimate`, and a hash (NOT raw text) of the prompt prefix.
